  "reference_number": "GAC0039",
  "remarks": "\nVasil BOZHKOV is an involved person under the Global Anti-Corruption Sanctions Regulations 2021 on the basis that he has been involved in serious corruption by offering or promising a financial advantage, namely a bribe, to a foreign public official, namely a Bulgarian public official, with the intention to reward that official for improperly performing a public function. \n",
